    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2019-10-29</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2019-11-05T12:59:44Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Congressional Budget Justification Transparency Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill requires federal agencies to make budget justification materials available to the public. The bill also requires the Office of Management and Budget to make certain details regarding the materials available to the public, including a list of the agencies that submit budget justification materials to Congress, the dates that the materials are submitted to Congress and posted online, and links to the materials.]]></text>
      </summary>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>53</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2020-09-14</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Passed House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2020-09-16T18:07:05Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Congressional Budget Justification Transparency Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill requires federal agencies to make budget justification materials available to the public. The bill also requires the Office of Management and Budget to make certain details regarding the materials available to the public, including a list of the agencies that submit budget justification materials to Congress, the dates that the materials are submitted to Congress and posted online, and links to the materials.]]></text>
      </summary>
